Hi, Thanks for reaching out.
This is Satish (co-founder) number. 7661933372

Hi,

Greetings!

I hope all well.

This is Sivasubramaniam from mymoneykarma heading South India Business.

We mymoneykarma is a Fintech, operating across Pan India and 70 cities.And we are almost tied up with 100+ Bank and NBFC across Pan India on lending all products

(HL, Mortgage,LAP,BL,BL, Auto loan,VL,Mechinary loan, Project loan etc).

We are in India from last 9 years and from October 2023 we are very aggressive working on Builders Service and Channel business on Home Loan service and fulfillment .

I would like to discuss business proposals ( TIEUP -B2B) & individually capacity on referral of customer looking for HL/Financial products , please let me know your convenient time and date to meet you in person.

Looking forward to hearing from you.

Regards/ 6364005174
